                     <interp inst="t18201028-68-person771" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a rigger. and live at Poplar. I know the prisoner, the last time I saw him with his wife, was in 1813. I afterwards met her under the Piazza in Covent Garden, and went home with her. The last time I saw her was in 1815 - she went by the name of 
               <persName id="t18201028-68-person772">
                  Mary 
